TrackList Class Reference

#include <Track.h>

List of all members.

Detailed Description

TrackList is a flat linked list of tracks supporting Add, Remove, Clear, and Contains, plus serialization of the list of tracks.

A list of TrackListNode items.

int TrackList::GetNumExportChannels ( bool  selectionOnly  ) 

Find out how many channels this track list mixes to.

This is used in exports of the tracks to work out whether to export in Mono, Stereo etc.

Parameters:
selectionOnly Whether to consider the entire track list or only the selected members of it
